channel.title: A few errors
channel.description:
my friend asked me to code a dodian server... so i downloaded dev v7, I went into the client.java and added a little code to it, I compiled it, and got these error's...
[code]client.java:9760: orphaned case case 252: ^ client.java:11740: illegal start of expression public String passHash(String password) { ^ 2 errors Files Compiled Successfully! Press any key to continue . . .[/code] and i was just wondering if some 1 new how to fix it... ?
thanks

item.title: A few errors
item.dc:creator: @Zach_93 Zach 93
item.description:
@Zach_93 wrote:

You have a case outside of a switch, and a method inside of another method. All of which is being caused by one missing closing bracket, I presume.
